{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"43":"General Behavior (Kitab Al-Adab)"},"section_detail":{"43":{"hadithnumber_first":4773,"hadithnumber_last":5274,"arabicnumber_first":4773,"arabicnumber_last":5274}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":5246,"arabicnumber":5246,"text":"Salim, citant son père (Ibn ‘Umar) رضي الله عنه, a dit (parfois il rapportait cela du Prophète ﷺ) : « Ne laissez pas de feu allumé dans vos maisons pendant que vous dormez. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (6293) Sahih Muslim (2015)"}],"reference":{"book":43,"hadith":474}}]}